      "title": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "i-City Theme Park"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "I-City is a dream-like high-tech business district illuminated by digital neon lights. The entire area is covered with advanced LED light and shadow technology. It is the first night sightseeing attraction in Malaysia built with LED lights. In the evening, the Digital Light Studio is shrouded in LED lights of different colors, as if entering a magical world of light and shadow, which is exquisite. In addition to the colorful neon lights, there are also theme parks such as a tropical rainforest-themed water park, a red carpet wax museum full of superstars, a 3D illusion art museum, space missions and other theme parks, as well as many fashionable shopping districts, which are very suitable for family travel."
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.3,
        "rating_count": 100
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Malaysia’s first LED-lit night attraction, glowing with digital neon brilliance."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Trendy shopping districts and theme parks make it perfect for family travel."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Attractions include a Red Carpet Wax Museum and 3D Illusion Art Museum."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Tropical rainforest water park offering fun and adventure for all ages."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Immersive Digital Light Studio — step into a magical world of color and light."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "At I-City, visitors can expect a dazzling experience filled with vibrant LED lights and digital art that transform the entire area into a glowing wonderland at night. The Digital Light Studio offers a magical display of colors and light, while attractions like the tropical rainforest water park, Red Carpet Wax Museum, and 3D Illusion Art Museum add fun and excitement for all ages. With its mix of futuristic lighting, exciting theme parks, and trendy shopping spots, I-City is a perfect destination for families looking for a lively and unforgettable outing."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "How to use: Show Mobile Ticket: Ticketing Counter"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Minimum age: All drivers must be at least 15 years old; minimum height: All drivers must be at least 140 cm tall. Before participating in the karting race, all drivers and passengers (or their parents/guardians) must complete a \"waiver form.\" Adult visitors should fill out the form for themselves, while parents or legal guardians must complete it for any accompanying children. Failure to comply will result in denied entry. All visitors must wear a face mask (head covering) and gloves. You may bring your own or purchase them upon entry. All visitors must follow all rules and instructions from the staff members at the kart racing park. Drivers and passengers must wear closed-toe shoes. Loose clothing such as dresses and skirts is not permitted. Long hair and scarves must be tied back in a ponytail and tucked behind the shirt or jacket. No outside food or drinks allowed. Smoking, e-cigarettes, and other vaping devices are strictly prohibited. Entry restrictions: For safety reasons, the following individuals are strictly prohibited from entering the karting race: disabled persons (OKU), wheelchair users, pregnant women, and individuals with heart disease or high blood pressure."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Cancellation Policy: No cancellation for this activity as per vendor policy"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "What’s included: Standard Admission"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Prohibited items: Outside food and beverages (except for infant formula) Smoking and e-cigarette use are strictly prohibited. Do not wear or carry jewelry and sharp objects. Avoid wearing or carrying loose items such as steel belt buckles, keychains, or hard objects in pockets."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: No outside food or drinks allowed No smoking, e-cigarettes, or other vaping devices allowed Strollers are not allowed. Prohibited to wear or carry jewelry and sharp items Do not wear or carry loose items such as metal belt buckles, key chains, or hard objects in pockets For safety reasons, the following people are strictly prohibited from entering SnoWalk by i-City: infants under 1 year old who cannot walk on their own, disabled individuals (OKU) with limited mobility, wheelchair users, and pregnant women. The above restrictions for entering i-City Theme Park's attractions are subject to i-City Theme Park's safety regulations and general terms and conditions. For further inquiries, please contact us directly."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "What’s included: SkyCity Fun Experience Package [Malaysian]"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: The inclusions a single entry to each attraction, which is valid on the same day only. Must comply with safety height and weight requirements and follow the terms, conditions and regulations of the theme park. Special groups: infant who cannot walk independently, people with disabilities, wheelchair users, pregnant women, etc., must follow the park's safety regulations when entering the park. For safety reasons, they are not allowed to enter the Snowwalk and Skycity Tower. Children are not allowed to enter the park alone and must be accompanied by a paying adult throughout the entire visit."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "What’s included: i-City Theme Park All Day Happiness Pass Entrance [Malaysian]"
